To commemorate the Nike TOMA Seoul event, Permanent Books has collaborated with Nike to create an art book titled â€œTotal of TOTAL 90â€, capturing everything about Nikeâ€™s legendary Total 90 series.

â€œTotal of TOTAL 90â€ features in-depth insights into Nikeâ€™s Total 90 productsâ€”iconic items that brought revolutionary design, technological innovation, and historical significance to the football industry. The book includes an archive of 90 Total 90 jerseys, lifestyle editorials, 90 magazine-style archive pages reminiscent of classic football publications, and posters showcasing the Korean national teamâ€”truly encapsulating the full legacy of Total 90.

With the recent global re-release of Total 90 drawing massive attention, this book combines a vast archive with an artistic reinterpretation, offering an unprecedented collection of content that adds to its unique value on a global scale.
